Simple HTTP TUI
----------------

Minimal cross-platform HTTP client TUI using notcurses.
Builds on Linux and Windows (via MinGW in WSL).

DEPENDENCIES
------------

Arch Linux (WSL):
    sudo pacman -S clang make pkgconf notcurses cmake git base-devel

MinGW toolchain (AUR):
    yay -S mingw-w64-gcc mingw-w64-crt mingw-w64-headers \
          mingw-w64-pkg-config mingw-w64-libdeflate mingw-w64-zlib

BUILD (LINUX)
-------------

    make linux

Result:
    bin/simple-http-tui

BUILD (WINDOWS CROSS-COMPILE)
-----------------------------

    make windows

This will:
    - generate MinGW toolchain file
    - clone notcurses
    - build notcurses for Windows
    - build bin/simple-http-tui.exe

RUN
---

    ./bin/simple-http-tui